<section class="module content">
  <div class="container">
    <p>

    Great stories are once sparks of inspiration. Synopsia is an archive that'll nudge you when you need the extra push. This site was initially built with a movie theme in mind. But whatever! If you need an inspiration for your story, be them novels or comic books, I hope you find something here. The name Synopsia is a shadow of the word "synopsis", which I soon later found out that it is also a name of a moth genus. So, yeah. Follow the moth when you want to go back to browsing. Click it, it'll bite.

    </p>
  </div>
</section>

